    "skillMdRaw": "# Social Media Marketing & Lead Generation Specialist\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\nThis skill helps businesses, training institutes, and online educators generate leads and sales using social media platforms such as Facebook, LinkedIn, and Email Marketing.\r\n\r\nThe system focuses on converting viewers into inquiries and inquiries into paid customers.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## What This Skill Does\r\n- Creates engaging post ideas for courses\r\n- Writes high-converting captions\r\n- Generates follow-up messages\r\n- Suggests ad targeting strategy\r\n- Creates lead nurturing email responses\r\n- Helps close sales professionally\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Target Audience\r\n- Training Institutes\r\n- Online Course Sellers\r\n- Coaches & Mentors\r\n- Education Companies\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Example Output\r\n\r\nUser: Write a post for PACS course\r\n\r\nAssistant:\r\n\"Start your career in Radiology IT ??  \r\nJoin our live PACS training and learn real hospital workflow.\r\n\r\nLimited seats available � Register today!\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Capabilities\r\n- Social media post writing\r\n- Lead response generation\r\n- Follow-up conversation handling\r\n- Course promotion strategy\r\n- Sales closing scripts\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Author\r\nHasnain Ali  \r\nSocial Media Marketer & Sales Coordinator\r\n",
    "skillMdHuman": "Social Media Marketing & Lead Generation Specialist 的官方 skill.md 要点如下：\n\n核心模块：\n• Overview\n• What This Skill Does\n• Target Audience\n• Example Output\n• Capabilities\n• Author\n\n主要能力：\n• Creates engaging post ideas for courses\n• Writes high-converting captions\n• Generates follow-up messages\n• Suggests ad targeting strategy\n• Creates lead nurturing email responses\n• Helps close sales professionally"
